訴。\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　110 　年　　11　　月　　26　　日\r\n                              書記官  劉淑慧","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDV/110%2c%e8%a8%b4%2c1031%2c20211126%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDV,110,訴,1031,20211126,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"訴","JNO":"1031","JDATE":"20211126","JTITLE":"清償借款"}